Package edu.gatech.mbse.transformations.sysml2milp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activator
    The activator class controls the plug-in life cycle
    InternalCorrespondences
    Internal correspondences between, e.g., resources and resource IDs, and instances of resources with their respective IDs, as well as indices in the allocation matrix.
    MILP2SysMLTransformation  
    StandardVariableNames
    This class contains a number of "standard" variables that the transformation knows of and specifically generates code for.
    SysML2MILPMappings
    Explicit mappings from SysML to MILP.
    SysML2MILPMappingsHelper
    This class contains a number of helper functions meant to outlie some complex traversal algorithms and keep them separate from the actual mappings performed.
    SysML2MILPTransformation
    SysML to MILP transformation.
    TransformationCache
    Class containing several static fields and getters and setters for lists of elements that are often required in the transformation, but require a complete traversal of the model.
    TransformationConfig
    Configuration of transformation.
    TransformationState
    State variables for transformation.
